shortDescription: Comfort and convenience come together perfectly in these leather slip-on casuals from George.  A memory foam insole and lightweight EVA midsole provide all the comfort you need, while the leather upper and TPR outsole give the shoes the durability you've come to expect.  The easy-on/easy-off design has two pull tabs, and elastic gore panels, making them easy to slip on.  A padded collar adds another layer of comfort.  Perfect with jeans, slacks or shorts, these are shoes you are sure to wear all the time!
